How to install Grisbi : 
=======================

Requirements:

 - GTK 1.x
 - Gnome 1.x development librairies
 - libxml or libxml2


Installation steps:

 - ./configure --prefix=/path/to/install/grisbi
 - make
 - make install

Grisbi will now be installed.  Just run <prefix>/bin/grisbi and have
fun !


